name: KOMPETE Token
public_notice:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract - which allows contract owners to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
KOMPETE Token is the official marketplace utility token for the KOMPETE Bazaar, an in-game secondary marketplace to buy and sell KOMPETE cosmetics.

KOMPETE is a team-based multiplayer game that's free to play. Initial game modes include Battle Royale, Kart Racing, Golf, & Basketball. More game modes are to be released in the future.

The developer of KOMPETE is Modernize Games.
